headline: XP Stock Sees Improved Relative Strength Rating
summary: In a welcome move, XP stock saw its Relative Strength Rating improve from 67 to 71 on Wednesday.    Can You Really Time The Stock Market?   IBD's unique rating tracks share price action with a 1 (worst) to 99 (best) score.

headline: Interactive Brokers Launches the Karta Visa Card
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., October 29, 2025--Interactive Brokers (Nasdaq: IBKR) is now offering eligible Interactive Brokers LLC clients the ability to open a Karta Visa card.
